          {
            "text": "ST. BASIL OF CAESAREA",
            "html": "<strong> <em>ST. BASIL OF CAESAREA</em></strong>"
          },
          {
            "text": "To Olympius.",
            "html": "<em>To Olympius</em>."
          },
          {
            "text": "As all the fruits of the season come to us in their proper time, flowers in spring, grain in summer, and apples in autumn, so the fruit for winter is talk."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
